List.Name: Italian Wine Gift Trio
List.Description:
For six Italian wines, take a look at the Viva Italia

Italy is one of the most diverse wine growing regions in Europe. Take a tour through the wine regions of the country as you sample varieties that have become hallmarks of Italian wine. This trio includes a fruity and sparkling Prosecco from Veneto, a juicy red from Tuscany and a spicy Nero d'Avola from Sicily.

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Santa Margherita Prosecco:
    This sparkling wine is clean and pleasantly fruity, with whiffs of rennet apples and peach blossoms. It has a delicate, balanced taste.

  • Mazzoni Tuscan Rosso:
    The Sangiovese provides a firm backbone and substantial body in this Tuscan, while the Merlot brings a luscious mouthfeel and lingering finish. It as a strong ruby red color and an intense bouquet of ripe dark berries.

  • Torresella Nero d'Avola:
    Very intense, this Nero d'Avola displays red and black berry fruit, spices, aromatic herbs and balsam. It is fresh and soft-textured with outstanding body.

  • Greet Sheet with descriptions of the three featured wines and recipe pairings for each. The description cards and recipes are perforated as 4x5 index cards to be torn off for future reference.

    Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Stonewall Kitchen Grilling & Wine Gift Set
List.Description:
Any grill master will enjoy this ultimate grilling gift set which includes Stonewall Kitchen's top selling and award winning Maple Chipotle Grille Sauce and Honey Barbecue Sauce. Also included are two fantastic spice rubs, Spicy Parmesan Corn Seasoning, and a silicone basting brush. Top the meal off with a bottle of Cline Zinfandel and Dancing Bull Cabernet and there you have it, a wonderful grilling and wine gift set!

Wine Gift Includes:

  • Cline Zinfandel:
    • This Zinfandel showcases a wide array of dark berry fruits, including black cherry and strawberry. Spice notes and a lasting finish of vanilla from oak aging and firm, supple tannins add complexity to this wine.
  • Dancing Bull Cabernet Sauvignon:
    • This Cabernet Sauvignon reveals complex flavors of black currant layered with dark spices with a hint of herbs, vanilla, and milk chocolate.
  • Maple Chipotle Grille Sauce:
    • This sauce is blended with firey chipotle peppers for a truly distinct sauce perfect for all your grilled meats.
  • Honey Barbecue Sauce:
    • This sauce adds just the right amount of sweet, smoky zest to barbecued meats.
  • Chicken and Pork Rub:
    • This rub adds flavorful dimension to chicken or pork. The savory combination of spices complements each other and enhances the flavor of your meal.
  • Spicy Parmesan Corn Seasoning:
    • Use this flavorful blend of parmesan cheese and spices to make your corn even more delicious. Seasoning can be used on corn-on-the-cob, popcorn or even a salad for that extra zing.
  • BBQ Basting Brush:
    • A must-have for any griller, this silicone basting brush will easily swoop up BBQ sauce. It has a large sized silicone brush head, silicone makes it super easy to clean, and an easy to grab wooden handle.

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

Wine gift sets & baskets may be packaged with the bottles separately boxed for their protection during shipment.

Pursuant to state laws in New York, gifts that contain both food and wine will be sent in two separate packages.

These come in a 100% Jute carrying tote, with a retractable six bottle insert. Delicioso!

California Dreaming Wine Gift Trio
List.Description:
Explore 3 additional California wine regions in our six bottle California Dreaming Big collection

We've gathered three top wines from select regions in California, representing a few grape varieties California does best. Wines include: Silverado Miller Ranch Sauvignon Blanc, Zinfandelic Amador County Old Vine Zinfandel and Buena Vista Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon.

Wine Gift Trio Includes:

  • Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc: Silverado Miller Ranch
    Napa Valley Sauvignon Blanc often delivers a rich texture akin to tropical fruit, while zingy acidity keeps it fresh and lively. The Miller Ranch Sauvignon Blanc shows attractive aromas of ripe grapefruit and honeydew melon, with spice and floral notes.

  • Sierra Foothills Zinfandel: Zinfandelic Amador County Old Vine
    The former Gold Country region of the Sierra Foothills provides an ideal Zinfandel habitat. Amador County in particular yields a bold Old Vine Zinfandel, with rich, bright raspberry and black cherry fruit, complemented by hints of earth and spice.

  • Sonoma County Cabernet Sauvignon: Buena Vista
    The diverse Sonoma County delivers a range of wines, but top among those is Cabernet Sauvignon. This well-balanced Cabernet offers generous fruit, with flavors of forest floor and musk that are supported by supple tannins and lead to a long, delicious finish.

  • Printed Insert that describes the featured wines

Due to the popularity of this gift, wines or vintages sometimes sell out. Should this happen, we will always substitute with the current vintage and wines with equal or greater value.

BRIX Chocolate for Bordeaux and Pinot Wine Gift Set
List.Description:
Chocolate and wine are an amazing duo, they truly bring out the best in each other. This gift set is the perfect tasting collection to indulge a wine and chocolate lover. Offering four chocolate bricks, each with a different cocoa content, BRIX chocolates are specifically blended to complement wine. The natural tannins in cocoa prime the palate for the tannins of the wine, allowing other flavors in the wine to shine. We carefully selected two wines to pair with a specific "brick" of chocolate.

Wine Gift Includes:

  • BRIX Chocolate Sampler:
    One 4 ounce brick each of extra dark 70%, medium dark 60%, smooth dark 54%, and milk 46%.

  • Domaines Baron Rothschild Reserve Speciale Bordeaux Rouge:
    Generous, rich and full-flavored on the palate, this wine has a long finish with hints of pepper and licorice.

  • Belle Glos Meiomi Pinot Noir:
    Three of the California's most sought after coastal growing regions brilliantly meld together in this deeply flavored, stylish and truly balanced Pinot Noir.
